  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《蓝色形态》目前第一章已经完成，将会尽快以抢先体验版与大家见面。后续章节仍在开发中，以后会持续更新。</h2><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578340/extras/36cd1a40f40a954df575bc5e8d293035.avif?t=1744426951\" width=380 height=77 /></span><br>战区硝烟弥漫，而都市中有些人在享受着糜烂生活。年轻的雇佣兵西诺，回到灯红酒绿的都市。进入一个俱乐部打工，那里聚集着一班上流社会的人。西诺来到这里的目的只有一个，向那个害死他重要之人的人复仇。然而就在西诺小心谋划着这件事时，某个高高在上的人一直紧盯着他……<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578340/extras/554151e282376224e90d2890185fcb0b.avif?t=1744426951\" width=380 height=77 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>煽情的剧情<br></li><li>现代都市背景<br></li><li>多张原创图像<br></li><li>足够备份的存档位</li></ul><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578340/extras/abf9b86a12086524b113d755facca99e.avif?t=1744426951\" width=380 height=77 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578340/extras/1349e3ce07530d4ce2ae928d90799456.avif?t=1744426951\" width=616 height=220 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578340/extras/10221c2435092adc1cb925066cd9b1a4.avif?t=1744426951\" width=616 height=220 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578340/extras/ac349eebe7fab390ca963bac1a31d0b9.avif?t=1744426951\" width=616 height=220 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578340/extras/c2c55975ea81f82683aff4d1518499f7.avif?t=1744426951\" width=616 height=220 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"